{"tool":"sql_query","args":{"query":"WITH earliest_prod AS (SELECT lot_id, plant_code, line_id, shift, build_date, release_status FROM production_quality_measurements ORDER BY build_date ASC, lot_id ASC LIMIT 1), earliest_cal AS (SELECT calibration_id, platform_code, engine_family, production_release_date, fuel_map_revision, ecu_checksum FROM powertrain_calibration_specs ORDER BY production_release_date ASC, calibration_id ASC LIMIT 1) SELECT CASE WHEN ep.build_date < ec.production_release_date THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END AS any_production_lot_earlier, ep.lot_id, ep.plant_code, ep.line_id, ep.shift, ep.build_date, ep.release_status, ec.calibration_id, ec.platform_code, ec.engine_family, ec.production_release_date, ec.fuel_map_revision, ec.ecu_checksum FROM earliest_prod ep CROSS JOIN earliest_cal ec","limit":10}}
{"answer":"Yes. The earliest production lot build_date is earlier than the earliest calibration production_release_date. Earliest production row: lot_id LOT-0001, plant_code PLT-APAC-2, line_id LN-07, shift C, build_date 2021-01-03, release_status Hold. Earliest calibration row: calibration_id CAL-0001, platform_code PX-1, engine_family I4T, production_release_date 2021-01-08, fuel_map_revision FMR-1.0, ecu_checksum 0x1A2B3C4D. Since 2021-01-03 < 2021-01-08, at least one production lot is earlier than the earliest calibration release."}

{"tool":"sql_query","args":{"query":"WITH fleet_count AS (
  SELECT COUNT(*) AS fleet_variant_count
  FROM vehicle_variant_configuration_specs
  WHERE lower(trim_level)=lower('Fleet')
), lfp_packs AS (
  SELECT pack_id, chemistry, estimated_range_km
  FROM battery_pack_module_specs
  WHERE lower(chemistry)=lower('LFP')
), lfp_count AS (
  SELECT COUNT(*) AS lfp_pack_count FROM lfp_packs
), top_lfp AS (
  SELECT pack_id, chemistry, estimated_range_km
  FROM lfp_packs
  ORDER BY CAST(estimated_range_km AS REAL) DESC, pack_id ASC
  LIMIT 1
)
SELECT fleet_count.fleet_variant_count, lfp_count.lfp_pack_count, top_lfp.pack_id, top_lfp.chemistry, top_lfp.estimated_range_km
FROM fleet_count, lfp_count, top_lfp","limit":10}}
{"answer":"Fleet vehicle variants: 173 (vehicle_variant_configuration_specs where trim_level='Fleet'). LFP battery packs: 258 (battery_pack_module_specs where chemistry='LFP'). Highest estimated_range_km among LFP packs: pack_id BAT-0738, chemistry LFP, estimated_range_km 798."}
